<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="47" type="habitat">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Habitat and ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="47">
Growing amongst granitic rocks and scattered shrubs on a steep hillside at 
<quantity metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.7" unit="m" value="2700.0">2700 m</quantity>
alt. (
